      '4.  **Internal Policy Updates:** Identify recurring issues across multiple contracts to inform updates to your standard templates and internal legal policies.',
      '5.  **Monitor Key Dates:** Leverage extracted key dates to set up reminders and proactively manage renewals and terminations, avoiding costly oversights.',
      '### Conclusion: Maximizing the Value of Your AI Insights',
      'An AI contract analysis report from ContractAnalyser is designed to be your intelligent co-pilot. It doesn\'t replace human legal expertise, but it significantly augments it, providing speed, accuracy, and depth of insight that was previously unattainable. By understanding the anatomy of these reports, you can unlock their full potential, mitigate risks more effectively, ensure stronger compliance, and make more informed strategic decisions for your business.',
